    <title>Markdown语法学习</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/05/12/Markdown/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/05/12/Markdown/</id>
    <published>2018-05-12T05:12:14.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-05-12T08:32:42.835Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="学习一波markdown语法（上）"><a href="#学习一波markdown语法（上）" class="headerlink" title="学习一波markdown语法（上）"></a>学习一波markdown语法（上）</h4><h3 id="1-标题语法"><a href="#1-标题语法" class="headerlink" title="1 标题语法"></a>1 标题语法</h3><p>​    Markdown支持两种标题的语法，Setext和atx形式。不过常用的还是Atx形式，在首行插入1个到6个#，对应标题标题1到6阶。就是#就代表<code>&lt;h1&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;</code>，2个就代表<code>&lt;h2&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;</code>，以此类推。</p><h3 id="2-修辞和强调"><a href="#2-修辞和强调" class="headerlink" title="2 修辞和强调"></a>2 修辞和强调</h3><p>Markdown 使用星号和底线来标记需要强调的区段。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Some of these words *are emphasized*.</span><br><span class="line">Some of these words _are emphasized also_. </span><br><span class="line">Use two asterisks for **strong emphasis**. </span><br><span class="line">Or, if you prefer, __use two underscores instead__.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>HTM输出为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;Some of these words &lt;em&gt;are emphasized&lt;/em&gt;. </span><br><span class="line">Some of these words &lt;em&gt;are emphasized also&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;Use two asterisks for &lt;strong&gt;strong   emphasis&lt;/strong&gt;. </span><br><span class="line">Or, if you prefer, &lt;strong&gt;use two underscores instead&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-列表"><a href="#3-列表" class="headerlink" title="3 列表"></a>3 列表</h3><p>​    无序列表里面使用星号、加号和减号作为项目的标记，值得注意的是中间一定要空一格。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">* 哈登</span><br><span class="line">+ 保罗</span><br><span class="line">- 阿里扎</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出HTML为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;ol&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;哈登&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;保罗&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;阿里扎&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/ol&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>游览器中表现为：</p><ul><li>哈登</li><li>保罗</li><li>阿里扎</li></ul><p>有序列表则使用数字接着一个英文句点，句点后面也需要空一格</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1. 塔克</span><br><span class="line">2. 巴莫特</span><br><span class="line">3. 周琦</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出HTMl为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;ul&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;塔克&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;巴莫特&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;li&gt;周琦&lt;/li&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/ul&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>游览器中表现为：</p><ol><li>塔克</li><li>巴莫特</li><li>周琦</li></ol><h3 id="4-链接"><a href="#4-链接" class="headerlink" title="4 链接"></a>4 链接</h3><p>Markdown支援两种形式的链接写法：行内和参考2种形式，都是使用角括号（[ ])来把文字转出链接。</p><p>行内形式是直接在后面用括号直接接上链接</p><p><code>This is a [blog](https://yyssll.top)</code></p><p>输出HTML为：</p><p><code>&lt;p&gt;this is an &lt;a href=&quot;https://yyssll.top&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</code></p><p>你也可以选择加上title属性：</p><p><code>This is a [blog](https://yyssll.top/&quot;with a Title&quot;).</code></p><p>输出HTML为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;a href=&quot;https://yyssll.top/&quot; title=&quot;with a title&quot;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参考形式的链接让你可以为链接定一个名称，之后你可以在文章中的其他地方定义该链接的内容：</p><p><a href="https://baidu.com/" title="baidu" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a></p><p><a href="http://google.com/" title="Google" target="_blank" rel="noopener">谷歌</a></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[百度][1]</span><br><span class="line">[谷歌][2]</span><br><span class="line">[1]:https://baidu.com/&quot;baidu&quot;</span><br><span class="line">[2]:https://google.com/&quot;Google&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出HTMl为：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;a href=&quot;https://baidu.com/&quot; title=&quot;baidu&quot;&gt;百度&lt;/a&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;a href=&quot;https://google.com/&quot; title=&quot;Google&quot;&gt;谷歌&lt;/a&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
